      "span_text": "Finally, we tested whether long-term depression (LTD) was altered in RAB39B down regulated cells, given the involvement of PICK1 in activity-dependent AMPAR endocytosis and LTD [CITATION_1] 40 . To this end, we assessed NMDARdependent LTD in shRab39b-, shScramble-and non-infected CA1 neurons (Fig. 8j) . After LTD induction (500 stimuli at 1 Hz, with postsynaptic depolarization at À 40 mV), AMPAR-mediated synaptic responses were equally depressed in the three conditions."
